# New feature page checklist

1. Feature folder: `src/app/features/<domain>/<feature>/`
2. Register route in `app.routes.ts` under `AppShellComponent` children.
3. If in sidebar: add `NavItem` in `sidebar-nav.config.ts` with matching `route`.
4. Placeholder only: reuse `PagePlaceholderComponent` + `data: { titleKey: 'pages.*' }`.
5. Form: `*.form.ts` + page; Table: `*.table.ts` + page; wire i18n under `forms.*` / `tables.*`.
6. Export types from `*.model.ts`; keep mock data in `*.mock-data.ts` beside feature.
